{
  "stem": "22750.5",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I tell you this story, and everything keeps-- and sometimes I change the mind.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my mind is not the same too, what I had.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I came out from the-- in 1944, I think, January or February, because it was wintertime.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was liberated and came out from the hole.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then there, from 1944, because the-- the war still was going on, yeah.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Even when I was liberated, it's no use even to think-- I had to go because I was younger.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the-- even the-- the-- the Russians start to mobilize with some [? headlock. ?] And they then took me.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was in the-- in the back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they took me to the army.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because some people, they survived like me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They went to the army.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They didn't come back from the army.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Survived Hitler, and then came-- because the war was going on still.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because the war was ending in 1945.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was the the end of the war.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, from the hiding?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- yeah, this I know because I came out from the hole.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And sit on-- on [? a headache. ?] And that, I took already.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because the shooting and some, from the guy who told me already, he knew it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And yes, this I find out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And matter of fact, it was already they call at that time, Partisans.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And some Partisans went by already.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The-- the-- the farm where-- where I lived.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were waiting for this, and anxious.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this was the time we find out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So some partisans told the farmer where you were in hiding?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They didn't know somebody there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nobody was trusted at the time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Only we find out it's already Russian Partisans.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
